# Git Basics 🔧

## Setup
git config --global user.name "Ganesh"
git config --global user.email "email"

## Daily Commands
git init          # start git
git status        # check changes
git add .         # stage all
git commit -m ""  # save snapshot
git push          # upload
git pull          # download
git clone <url>   # copy repo

## Workflow
Working → git add → Staging
Staging → git commit → Saved
Saved   → git push  → GitHub
